Introducing the Release Celebration Gacha!

This Gacha includes only 2★ or higher characters!
Pull from the 10x Gacha to get a guaranteed 3★ or higher character!
4★ characters that are pulled for the first time come with a Costume.
Getting a Costume unlocks the option in the Costume Shop to make the same one or color variants of it for other characters.

Receive 1 Release Celebration Gacha Sticker for every character obtained from the Release Celebration Gacha.
Exchange 300 Release Celebration Gacha Stickers for one of the characters listed in the Release Celebration Gacha Sticker Exchange.
gachaInformation.description:
•Once Daily Gacha can only be pulled using Paid Crystals.
•A valid COLORFUL+ can be used to pull from the Once Daily Gacha up to twice a day.
•Once Daily Gacha resets at 4:00AM PST daily.
•When pulling from this Gacha, Free Crystals will be used first where applicable.
•Characters from this Gacha will be in a pre-Upgraded state.
•Duplicate characters may be pulled from this Gacha.
•Duplicate characters are automatically sent to the Green Room.
•Gacha characters are pulled one at a time based on existing drop rates. The drop rates therefore do not mean that, for example, characters with a drop rate of 1% are guaranteed to appear once every 100 pulls.
•When pulling from the 10x gacha, if no 3★ or higher characters are pulled, the tenth slot will be pulled again using guaranteed slot drop rates.
•Drop rates can be viewed from the drop rates tab.
•Stats and skills of new characters can be viewed by tapping the Character Details button on the Gacha screen.
•After starting the Gacha, even if the app should force-quit or be disconnected without displaying the Gacha results screen, pulled characters will be saved and viewable either on the Characters screen or in the Green Room.
•Release Celebration Gacha Stickers are valid for exchange until January 16, 2022 at 2:59PM PST. After this period, they will be converted into an equivalent number of Wish Pieces.
•The Gacha schedule is subject to change without notice.
